data.description: Nestled within the picturesque and sought-after Woodland Park neighborhood, this exceptional property presents a remarkable opportunity for those seeking a blend of timeless craftsmanship, spacious living, and the chance to infuse their personal touch. 5 beds, 2.5 baths, skylit foyer, marble fireplace in living room, sunroom w vaulted wood ceiling, dining room with bookcases, spacious kitchen, family room with high ceilings. 3rd-floor owner's suite boasts skylights and large bathroom. Lower level perfect for office/gym.While this residence's charm lies in its classic allure, it's primed for your creative vision. A palette of possibilities awaits, inviting you to infuse your personal style and modern updates while retaining the foundational elegance that defines this Craftsman gem.
